        <mxCell id="n121" value="" style="rhombus;html=1;fillColor=#0F1723;strokeColor=#0F1723;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1612" y="704" width="16" height="16" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="n122" value="&lt;b&gt;M6 &amp;#183; W30&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:9px;color:#5A6472&quot;&gt;Migration engine live&lt;br/&gt;5 Feb 2027&lt;/font&gt;" style="rounded=1;arcSize=18;html=1;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#DFE4EA;fontSize=10;fontColor=#0F1723;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;spacing=3;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1536" y="652" width="168" height="48" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="n123" value="" style="line;strokeWidth=1;html=1;strokeColor=#B9C4D0;direction=north;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1620" y="700" width="1" height="10" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="n124" value="" style="rounded=1;arcSize=8;html=1;fillColor=#0F1723;strokeColor=none;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="40" y="804" width="1580" height="60" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="n125" value="The rule that holds across every phase" style="text;html=1;fontSize=13;fontStyle=1;fontColor=#FFFFFF;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="60" y="812" width="900" height="20" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="n126" value="An approved request becomes a CONFIGURATION ROW executed by ONE generic engine. MFT, API, mashup or event — it never generates a new Boomi component per interface." style="text;html=1;fontSize=12;fontColor=#B9C4D0;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="60" y="832" width="1500" height="24" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="n127" value="" style="rounded=1;arcSize=6;html=1;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#DFE4EA;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="40" y="886" width="1580" height="120" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="n128" value="Decisions that need a named owner BEFORE Phase 0 starts" style="text;html=1;fontSize=13;fontStyle=1;fontColor=#8F1D17;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="60" y="894" width="1000" height="20" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="n129" value="1.  May the MVP provision a PRODUCTION interface on username + password + 2FA?  Recommendation: no — gate Production until SSO and the full pre-check engine land in Phase 4 (week 19)." style="text;html=1;fontSize=11.5;fontColor=#3D4653;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="60" y="916" width="1540" height="24" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="n130" value="2.  Phase 4 (SSO &amp;amp; governance) overlaps the Phase 3 mashup build and lands ~3 months out. The API estate runs on MVP-grade controls from week 6 to 19. Keep it non-production until P4, or pull ADM-04 forward." style="text;html=1;fontSize=11.5;fontColor=#3D4653;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="60" y="942" width="1540" height="24" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="n131" value="3.  Will the mashup engine (Phase 3) be held to DECLARATIVE composition?  The first request for an arbitrary script inside a mashup arrives in the back half of the phase. Decide now, not then." style="text;html=1;fontSize=11.5;fontColor=#3D4653;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="60" y="968" width="1540" height="24" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
</mxfile>
